description.narrative: This activity will enhance the ability of the Tuvalu Ministry of Fisheries and Trade to ensure that Tuvalu's fisheries recources are sustainable and well managed, and that the social and economic returns from fisheries revenue are maximised. This business case seeks funding for scoping and design recommendations which will inform design of the activity as a whole and the subsequent detailed business case.
